      <title>英国央行认为对冲基金国债基差交易带来更多风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/boe-sees-more-risk-in-hedge-fund-short-positons-in-us-treasuries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行加大了对对冲基金做空美国国债期货的警告力度，称其净头寸衡量标准目前高于 2020 年 3 月“急需现金”危机之前的规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/boe-sees-more-risk-in-hedge-fund-short-positons-in-us-treasuries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 10:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券反弹动摇，股市保持降息信心：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/asia-stocks-to-gain-treasuries-rally-on-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易员加大押注，央行行长正在准备全球政策转向降息，股市恢复上涨。随着美国10年期国债收益率升至4.2%，债券涨势陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/asia-stocks-to-gain-treasuries-rally-on-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:47:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称哈马斯袭击前没有明显的贸易异常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/israel-says-it-found-no-trade-abnormalities-before-hamas-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列证券管理局表示，在哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击之前的几天里，没有发现任何需要进一步调查的重大股票交易异常情况，这是对美国撰写的一篇引起公众轩然大波的研究论文中的说法的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/israel-says-it-found-no-trade-abnormalities-before-hamas-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 20:49:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
